        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Their managed WordPress platform, EasyWP, received speed improvements. The Starter plan begins at a price point that makes premium WordPress hosting accessible to hobbyists and freelancers. Automatic backups, easy staging, and one-click restores are baked right in.",
