          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shared hosting plans (Stellar, Stellar Plus) now run on an updated cPanel with faster load times and cleaner navigation. If you've used cPanel before, the learning curve is zero. If you haven't, Namecheap's interface makes it intuitive.",
            "marks": []
          }
