      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For users who've outgrown shared hosting, Namecheap's VPS plans offer root access, dedicated resources, and scalable configurations. The pricing stays competitive compared to alternatives like DigitalOcean or Linode.",
